1.3
log
@if -c0 don't touch comments
(took me like 3 hours to implement; this code is ugly)
@
text
@/**	$MirBSD$ */
/*	$OpenBSD: pr_comment.c,v 1.5 2003/06/12 01:07:27 deraadt Exp $	*/

